dct_title_s: Automobile routes from Los Angeles to Sunland, La Crescenta, and La Cañada
dct_description_sm: Automobile Club of Southern California ; H.P.H.
Relief shown by hachures and spot heights.
Coordinates approximate and based on Greenwich meridian.
Oriented with north toward upper right.
Shows city plans, roads, railroads, waterways.
Indicates distances from Pasadena and Hollywood.
Includes table of distances "Taken by Warner Auto Meter."
Numbered 63 in lower left and 4 in bottom margin.
Belongs to a series of strip maps showing roads in California.
